1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Join Josh for celebrity interviews, special event coverage, and intimate tours of New York hotspots! This episode features Johnny Rozsa's "Untouched" photo exhibit, Alias Restaurant, and playwright Charles Busch.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Join Josh for celebrity interviews, special event coverage, and intimate tours of New York hotspots! This episode features Simon and Nick of Duran Duran, "Sex in Drag" author Greg Scarnici, and controversial musician Ari Gold.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Join Josh for celebrity interviews, special event coverage, and intimate tours of New York hotspots! This episode features Bravo's Tabatha Coffey, Bob Pontarelli of Industry, and Tom Viola of Broadway Cares/Equity Fights AIDS.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Join Josh for celebrity interviews, special event coverage, and intimate tours of New York hotspots! This episode features pop star Kimberley Locke, Justin Luke and Paige Turner of "So You Think You Can Drag", and the Pop-Up Museum of Queer History.

imdb.plot outline: Josh Rosenzweig, co-host of "Here with Josh & Sara," returns with his own original series. Filmed on location throughout New York City, Josh turns the traditional talk show format on its head. From celebrity interviews to premiere VIP events, Josh brings his own brand of humor and his intense love of New York City to the small screen, treating fans to a unique and entertaining spin on pop culture.
